(36,'Align Weapon','Weapon becomes good, evil, lawful, or chaotic.','Align weapon makes a weapon good, evil, lawful, or chaotic, as you choose. A weapon that is aligned can bypass the damage reduction of certain creatures, usually outsiders of the opposite alignment. This spell has no effect on a weapon that already has an alignment, such as a holy sword.\nYou can\'t cast this spell on a natural weapon, such as an unarmed strike.\nWhen you make a weapon good, evil, lawful, or chaotic, align weapon is a good evil, lawful, or chaotic spell, respectively.','1sa','Touch',1,NULL,'','1 min','Will neg(h,o)','Yes(h,o)',5,1,NULL,NULL),
