(982,'Fog Cloud','Fog obscures vision.','A bank of fog billows out from the point you designate. The fog obscures all sight,including darkvision, bevond 5 feet. A creature within 5 feet has concealment (attacks have a 20% miss chance). Creatures farther away have total concealment (50%miss chance, and the attacker can\'t use sight to locate the target). A moderate wind (11+ mph) disperses the fog in 4 rounds a strong wind 21+mph) disperses the fog in 1 round The spell does not function underwater.','1sa','Med',4,NULL,'','10 min','None','No',5,2,NULL,NULL),
