(1862,'Regenerate','Subject\'s severed limbs grow back, cures 4d8+1 points of damage.','The subject\'s severed body members (fin gers, toes, hands, feet, arms, legs, tails, or even heads of multiheaded creatures), broken bones, and ruined organs grow back.After the spell is cast, the physical regeneration is complete in 1 round if the severed members are present and touching the creature. It takes 2d10 rounds otherwise. Regenerate also cures 4ds points of damage +1 point per caster level (maximum +35), rids the subject of exhaustion and/or fatigue, and eliminates all nonlethal damage the subject has taken. It has no effect on nonliving creatures (including undead).','3 frs','Touch',1,NULL,'','Inst','Fort neg(h)','Yes(h)',5,6,NULL,NULL),
